# Project Context Memory

Use project docs and existing code as the primary source of truth before asking user to repeat context.

## First sources to check

- `README.md`
- `.cursor/PROJECT_CONTEXT.md` (if present)
- current `app/`, `templates/`, `static/` implementation

## Communication defaults

- Do not ask the user to re-explain what already exists in code/docs.
- Ask questions only when there is a real ambiguity that blocks a safe change.
- Keep replies concise and practical.

## Implementation defaults

- Reuse existing architecture and naming.
- Prefer incremental edits over rewrites.
- Preserve existing behavior unless user explicitly requests a change.
- After edits, quickly verify that the updated paths still work together.

